<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV5">
<l>niṉṟiyaṅku moṉṟalāvu rukkaṭō ṟumāviyāy</l>
<l>oṉṟiyuṭka lantuniṉṟa niṉṉataṉmai yiṉṉateṉ</l>
<l>ṟeṉṟumyārkku meṇṇiṟanta vātiyāyniṉ ṉuntivā</l>
<l>yaṉṟunāṉmu kaṟpayanta vātitēva ṉallaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Supreme Lord whom no one can fathom at any time</l>
<l>claiming that such is Your nature of uniting and mingling together [with the people],</l>
<l>Being the soul in each of the many bodies of static [and] moving [creatures]!</l>
<l>Are you not the primordial Lord who begot out of Your navel the four-faced [Brahmā]</l>
<l rend="indent">in the past?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
